This is a program somewhat similar to varniststat which monitors a set
of varnish servers.  A companion program, webnoded.pl, must be
installed on each of the varnish servers and run by xinetd.  When you
telniet in to port 7600, the webnoded.pl program responds to commands
to dump varnish stats.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
##  this is the config file for xinted (stored in /etc/xinted.d/webnoded)

service unlisted
{
        type            = UNLISTED
        socket_type     = stream
        protocol        = tcp
        wait            = no
        user            = root
        server          = <path-to-webnoded>/webnoded.pl
        port            = 7600
        id              = webnoded-stream
}
------------------------------------------------------------------------
